Show Device status:df -h
Show Active Process:ps -ef
Show Memory:free  
Show Cpu:more /proc/cpuinfo
Show USB Devices:lsusb
Show TCP Network Connection:netstat -tn
Show UDP Network Connection:netstat -un
Show TCP Listener:netstat -tln
Show UDP Listener:netstat -uln
Show Route Table:netstat -rn
Show Loaded Kernel Modules:lsmod
Show NewCS Info:(echo ''; sleep 1; echo 'version'; sleep 1; echo 'uptime'; sleep 1; echo 'quit') | nc 127.0.0.1 3001
Show NewCS User Info:(echo ''; sleep 1; echo 'users'; sleep 1; echo 'quit') | nc 127.0.0.1 3001
Show NewCS Card Info:(echo ''; sleep 1; echo 'cards'; sleep 1; echo 'quit') | nc 127.0.0.1 3001
Show NewCS Subscrition Info:(echo ''; sleep 1; echo 'sub -1'; sleep 1; echo 'quit') | nc 127.0.0.1 3001
Show MGcamd info:cat /tmp/mgstat.info
Show MGcamd share:cat /tmp/mgshare.info
